<?php $pageTitle='About | Local Legends Orlando'; require '../includes/header.php'; ?><section class="page-intro"><p class="eyebrow">Our hometown perspective</p><h1>We believe local stories have the power to bring us closer.</h1></section><section class="prose section"><h2>Our mission</h2><p>Local Legends Orlando celebrates the entrepreneurs, organizations, and small businesses that make Central Florida extraordinary. We share the real stories behind the signs, storefronts, and bright ideas.</p><h2>Our vision</h2><p>We’re building a more connected Orlando—one where great work is seen, neighbors become regulars, and community pride has a place to grow.</p><h2>Why local matters</h2><p>When a local business thrives, it creates a ripple: jobs, generosity, craft, gathering spaces, and opportunity. Those ripples are worth knowing by name.</p><h2>Want to be featured?</h2><p>We’d love to learn about your work and the people you serve. <a href="<?=url('get-featured/')?>">Tell us your story</a>; our editorial team reviews every submission with care.</p></section><?php require '../includes/footer.php'; ?>
